window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Aiden and his team have triumphed, earning the right to represent the Craesti Kingdom in the Internation Tournament of Champions. They are on their way to Monster Island, home of the Ashkhas nation, where they will compete against the elites of four other nations. Will they be able to return home in glory, or will they slink back in defeat? Will Chaos interfere here as well?</p>"; 
